# Zola site: build output + content generated from vignette/*.html.md by
# `just site-build`. Authored pages (_index.md section landings, about.md) are
# kept; the generated vignette pages in section subdirs are not.
site/public/
# Rustdoc built locally by `just site-rustdoc` into static/ for preview/checks.
# CI builds it fresh into public/rustdoc (see .github/workflows/pages.yml).
site/static/rustdoc/
# Starlight R docs built locally by `just site-r` into static/ for preview.
# CI builds it fresh into public/r (see .github/workflows/pages.yml).
site/static/r/
site/content/**/*.md
!site/content/**/_index.md
!site/content/about.md
.claude/worktrees/
